==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Steepness
<hw>Steep"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Quality or state of
being steep; precipitous declivity; <as>as, the <ex>steepness</ex>of a
hill or a roof</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Height; loftiness.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Chapman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Steep-up</ent>⟦br⟧
